{"tid":285220,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★團體要求暫緩修訂富戶政策 !","createTime":"2017-06-15T15:13:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-19T06:52:12.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"47f423b931a01db2884a4d97e25af1629c2c3234","tid":285220,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T15:13:31.000Z","msg":"公屋聯會20多名代表趁房委會開會, 到房委會總部請願, 要求暫緩修訂富戶政策, 重新啟動公眾諮詢.<br />\n        聯會指, 公屋供求失衡, 罪不在於公屋富戶, 而是政府過去政策失誤, 但房委會在未經廣泛諮詢, 就倉卒修訂富戶政策, 向居民開刀, 質疑是企圖轉移視線.<br />\n        聯會批評, 收緊政策可能迫使年輕家庭成員要刪除戶籍, 違背了公屋戶老有所依的理念, 亦漠視公屋藏富於民的功能, 影響住戶的退休計劃, 又認為, 安排會製造更多置業需求, 進一步推高樓價, 要求暫緩修訂政策.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/files/images/20170602141232_170602151957_m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Ffiles%2Fimages%2F20170602141232_170602151957_m.jpg&h=79c92be5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsId=20170602141232\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Flive.aspx%3FNewsId%3D20170602141232&d=T%2FS5IpksPVt9v4yNcky7Fm6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=7c7bcea0\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsId=20170602141232</a>"},{"pid":"db53e8c70a90c54016189a15abf96ab0be98674c","tid":285220,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T15:14:11.000Z","msg":"蓋老母等收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5c348faf89c0a199a4fed39627b3e180e095186","tid":285220,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T15:16:56.000Z","msg":"呢個pk政策搞到早幾個月d床位租貴曬，要瞓M記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=